J.png&h=75006aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屎忽鬼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q18SNdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq18SNdR.png&h=e02a3280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n垃圾刺成員 <br />\nLma Lma  ||  DDR Ddr DDr DDR 還債仔 ||  Forbes 冰科 聖城咖哩 <br />\nWhite 白仔 小白 白帝 少煮  ||   Murray 揸ass 屎忽鬼  DJ<br />\nPop 廢老pop 波波  ||   Walker 芹菜  ||  Bertans 毒瘤<br />\nMills 毛巾  ||  Belinelli 意粉  ||  Poeltl 大白腸<br />\nGay 基    ||  Cunningham 工兵王  || Metu 美圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">垃圾刺圍爐po守則 :<br />\n1.魚腩最忌有自信<br />\n2.垃圾係唔屌唔得嘅，垃圾無一個讚得<br />\n3.永遠唔好存有贏波希望去睇垃圾廁既波<br />\n4.平安鐘是必須<br />\n5.倒水只會遲到不會缺席<br />\n6.三分射手們骰仔中六先入<br />\n7.廢過tank隊，輸30分係基本</span><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n刺撚兩大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. M記嘉大(已潛水)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/091003_617a7514eda6c7c606fb24500d7bbd54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F091003_617a7514eda6c7c606fb24500d7bbd54.png&h=466fdbc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 會然Spurs_Leonard改名<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSoxvg8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSoxvg8.gif&h=145b3c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n開PO專用  <a href=\"https://goo.gl/a7zBiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fa7zBiA&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8hD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJ